      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，join 是 local 主动发起，remote 收到后回复 peer，完成 handshake。这个阶段要用 critical 区块标注出来，表示这是关键阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "join",
        "peer",
        "handshake",
        "critical"
